<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l4">dıe neẅlıch <expan>ergange<ex>n</ex></expan> haben . <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l5"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> des <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ / Bıttend </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l6">eẅr gute <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / Ob Jr hınfür ıcht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre von </ab>
