<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l9">als vıl eẅch füklıch ſey 
<add><ab facs="#facs_442_r1l8">aber </ab></add> ın <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet dıe </ab>
