</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_442" id="220r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Eger</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns von der Hussen
                                <expan>lewff<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>gelegenh<ex>eit</ex></expan>, wie sich die newlich
                                <expan>ergange<ex>n</ex></expan> haben,
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> des <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, bittend ewr gute
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, ob ir hinfür icht
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre von
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>lewff<ex>en</ex></expan> erfüret <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gewar
                        wurdet, daz ir uns davon, als vil ewch füklich sey, <add>aber</add> in
                                <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet; die bottenlon wellen wir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beczaln. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
